---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Anasayfa" activePage="home">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Yenipak<br>Ambalaj</h1>
      <p>1997'den günümüze, profesyonel çalışma anlayışı ile Yenipak, sonuca götüren çözümler üretir.</p>
      <a class="btn-primary" href="/urunler">Tüm Ürünler</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="form-section">
    <div class="form-inner">
      <h2>Bilgi & Sipariş Talep Formu</h2>
      <form class="form-grid" id="quick-form">
        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Ad-Soyad *" required>
        <input type="text" name="company" placeholder="Şirket *" required>
        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email *" required>
        <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Telefon *" required>
        <input type="text" name="message" placeholder="Mesajınız">
        <button type="submit" class="btn-send">Gönder</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--white)">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">Neden Yenipak Ambalaj? <a class="section-tag" href="/kurumsal">Hakkımızda</a></h2>
      <div class="cards-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/nsplsh_1c61f55557634011bd1fac15234ac68c~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_312,h_207,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/nsplsh_1c61f55557634011bd1fac15234ac68c~mv2.jpg" alt="Müşteri Memnuniyeti">
          <div class="card-body"><h3>Müşteri Memnuniyeti</h3><p>ISO standartları çerçevesindeki süreçlerimizle birincil hedefimiz müşteri memnuniyetinin tahsis edilmesi ve taleplerinin kaliteden ödün vermeden hızlı şekilde sonuçlandırılmasıdır.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/ac31a9_2933154e5de9430eb8f113021356a6a7~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_314,h_169,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/ac31a9_2933154e5de9430eb8f113021356a6a7~mv2.jpg" alt="Ücretsiz Teslimat">
          <div class="card-body"><h3>İstanbul İçi Ücretsiz Teslimat</h3><p>İstanbul içi müşterilerimiz için ürünleriniz sevkiyat planlamasına alınır ve ücretsiz olarak adresinize firmamızın araçlarıyla teslim edilir.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d948a3_124de12b9aef4a40b6e490fcf90e7a8c~mv2.jpeg/v1/fill/w_314,h_177,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/d948a3_124de12b9aef4a40b6e490fcf90e7a8c~mv2.jpeg" alt="Çözümler">
          <div class="card-body"><h3>Sonuca Giden Çözümler Üretiriz</h3><p>Geniş müşteri portföyümüz ve sektördeki uzmanlığımız sayesinde müşterilerimiz için tedarikçi olmanın ötesinde danışman rolünü üstlenerek alternatif çözümler üretiriz.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="stats-section">
    <div class="stats-inner">
      <h2>Rakamlarla Yenipak Ambalaj</h2>
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div><span class="stat-num">8000 m²</span><div class="stat-label">Hizmet Alanı</div></div>
        <div><span class="stat-num">1997</span><div class="stat-label">Kuruluş Tarihi</div></div>
        <div><span class="stat-num">500 Ton/Ay</span><div class="stat-label">Bobin Dilimleme Kapasitesi</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>Yenipak Ambalaj, 8 Eylül 1997 tarihinde Polinas A.Ş.'nin ana bayii olarak kurulmuştur. Başta gıda ambalajı olmak üzere çeşitli filmlerin alım satım ve dilimleme işlemlerini yapmaktadır.</p>
        <p>2004'ten itibaren Hadımköy'deki 8000 m² kapalı tesisinde faaliyetlerini sürdürmekte, 49 personel ve 20 makine ile hizmet vermektedir.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--gray-bg)">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title">Hizmetlerimiz</h2>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card"><h3>Dilme</h3><p>Modern dilimleme makinelerinde fason dilimleme hizmeti.</p><ul><li>OPP</li><li>CPP</li><li>Metalize</li><li>Bariyer Film</li><li>PET</li><li>PVC</li><li>Kağıt</li><li>PE</li></ul></div>
        <div class="service-card"><h3>Perfore</h3><p>Makro ve ya mikro perforeli işleriniz itina ile yapılır.</p><ul><li>CPP perforasyonu</li><li>OPP perforasyonu</li><li>PE perforesi</li></ul></div>
        <div class="service-card"><h3>Korona Atma</h3><p>Sıfır dyn korona seviyesi olan malzemelere dahi 40 dyn yakın korona atılabilir.</p><ul><li>OPP</li><li>CPP</li><li>Metalize</li><li>PET</li><li>PVC</li><li>PE</li></ul></div>
        <div class="service-card"><h3>Tabakalama</h3><p>Fason tabaka – çıkrık işleriniz itina ile yapılır.</p><ul><li>Tabakalı ürün satışı</li><li>Fason çıkrıkta tabakalama</li><li>Giyotin kesim</li></ul></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background:var(--white);text-align:center">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:center">Kalite Belgelerimiz</h2>
      <div class="certs-grid">
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/ac31a9_37c1ed175b4142e4932591e5bc1c4614~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_347,h_232,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/ac31a9_37c1ed175b4142e4932591e5bc1c4614~mv2.png" alt="ISO 9001"></div>
        <div class="cert-card"><img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/ac31a9_7d19ad361578471ea8aa90f47a05b101~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_414,h_276,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/ac31a9_7d19ad361578471ea8aa90f47a05b101~mv2.jpg" alt="ISO 45001"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  .hero { position: relative; min-height: 420px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0e4a8a 0%, #1a5fa8 50%, #2a7fd4 100%); display: flex; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: url('https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d948a3_c9ba26606c5f46e68093f29b42c3db1c~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_980,h_425,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/d948a3_c9ba26606c5f46e68093f29b42c3db1c~mv2.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; opacity: 0.22; }
  .hero-content { position: relative; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; z-index: 1; }
  .hero h1 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 52px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--white); line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 16px; text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .hero p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); font-size: 17px; max-width: 480px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 28px; }

  /* FORM */
  .form-section { background: var(--blue-dark); padding: 48px 24px; }
  .form-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .form-section h2 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center; }
  .form-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 2fr auto; gap: 12px; align-items: end; }
  .form-grid input { width: 100%; padding: 11px 14px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 4px; color: var(--white); font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; outline: none; transition: border .2s; }
  .form-grid input::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .form-grid input:focus { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .btn-send { background: var(--accent); color: var(--white); border: none; padding: 11px 28px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; cursor: pointer; transition: background .2s; height: 42px; white-space: nowrap; }
  .btn-send:hover { background: #c8881a; }

  /* CARDS */
  .cards-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 28px; }
  .card { background: var(--gray-bg); border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; transition: transform .25s, box-shadow .25s; }
  .card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(26,95,168,0.12); }
  .card img { width: 100%; height: 180px; object-fit: cover; }
  .card-body { padding: 22px; }
  .card-body h3 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-dark); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .card-body p { font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-light); }

  /* STATS */
  .stats-section { background: var(--blue); padding: 56px 24px; }
  .stats-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .stats-inner h2 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--white); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--white); display: block; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-top: 4px; }
  .about-text { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); line-height: 1.9; font-size: 14.5px; max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .about-text p { margin-bottom: 14px; }

  /* SERVICES */
  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .service-card { background: var(--white); border-radius: 10px; padding: 28px 22px; border-top: 4px solid var(--blue); transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s; }
  .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(26,95,168,0.1); }
  .service-card h3 { font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-dark); margin-bottom: 14px; padding-bottom: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .service-card p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .service-card ul { list-style: none; font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--text-light); line-height: 2; }
  .service-card ul li::before { content: '• '; color: var(--blue); font-weight: bold; }

  /* CERTS */
  .certs-grid { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 40px; }
  .cert-card { background: var(--gray-bg); border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; width: 280px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); transition: transform .2s; }
  .cert-card:hover { transform: scale(1.02); }
  .cert-card img { width: 100%; height: 190px; object-fit: cover; }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
    .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cards-grid, .services-grid, .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 30px; }
    .form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  document.getElementById('quick-form')?.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    const form = e.target as HTMLFormElement;
    const data = new FormData(form);
    const body = encodeURIComponent(
      'Ad-Soyad: ' + data.get('name') +
      '\nŞirket: ' + data.get('company') +
      '\nTelefon: ' + data.get('phone') +
      '\n\nMesaj: ' + data.get('message')
    );
    window.location.href = 'mailto:satis@yenipak.com?subject=Bilgi%20%26%20Sipari%C5%9F%20Talebi&body=' + body;
  });
</script>
